;HELIX
THE EXTENDED REGIONS BEFORE A-HELIX (RESIDUES A 20 TO A 25
AND B 20 TO B 25) AND AFTER A-HELIX (RESIDUES A 43 TO A 46
AND B 43 TO B 46) ARE MORE FLEXIBLE.  THE STRUCTURE IN
THESE REGIONS IS ILL-DEFINED AND THE ATOMS HAVE HIGH
TEMPERATURE FACTORS.
;
